data.description: Welcome to 1497 Elderberry Rd, Suffolk VA! Nestled in the serene area of Parkside at Bennetts Creek, this charming 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom with oversized attached garage home offers a perfect blend of comfort and style. Spacious living area with lots of natural light,  making it easy for relaxation or entertaining guests. The modern kitchen boasts sleek counter tops, stainless appliances, big island, and ample storage, making meal preparation a breeze. Retreat after a long day to the cozy primary bedroom with vaulted ceilings, spacious walk in closet, and private balcony. Bonus room you can make into 5th bedroom, playroom, and or media/game room. Don't forget to enjoy access to the community pool and clubhouse, perfect for enjoying sunny days and social gatherings. Conveniently located near shops, restaurants, and parks, this home presents an opportunity for effortless living in Suffolk. Don't miss your chance to make this your new home sweet home.
